{
  "video_id": "M5PiTCwoQRo",
  "title": "What if gentrification was about healing communities instead of displacing them? | Liz Ogbu",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13370.0,
      "end_time": 16590.0,
      "text": "I grew up in a family of social scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17400.0,
      "end_time": 19535.0,
      "text": "but I was the weird child who drew."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20108.0,
      "end_time": 21354.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21796.0,
      "end_time": 25701.0,
      "text": "From making sketches of the models in my mom&#39;s Sears catalog ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27187.0,
      "end_time": 29963.0,
      "text": "to a bedroom so full of my craft projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29987.0,
      "end_time": 32202.0,
      "text": "that it was like my own personal art gallery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33164.0,
      "end_time": 34973.0,
      "text": "I lived to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36909.0,
      "end_time": 40652.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think anyone in my family was surprised when I became an architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41844.0,
      "end_time": 44129.0,
      "text": "But to be honest with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44153.0,
      "end_time": 46607.0,
      "text": "the real foundation of the architect I became"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46631.0,
      "end_time": 49283.0,
      "text": "was not laid in that bedroom art gallery"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49307.0,
      "end_time": 52346.0,
      "text": "but by the conversations around my family&#39;s dinner table."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53540.0,
      "end_time": 57927.0,
      "text": "There were stories of how people lived and connected to one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57951.0,
      "end_time": 61644.0,
      "text": "from the impact of urban migration on a village in Zambia"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61668.0,
      "end_time": 63196.0,
      "text": "to the complex health care needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63220.0,
      "end_time": 65470.0,
      "text": "of the homeless in the streets of San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66574.0,
      "end_time": 67764.0,
      "text": "Now, it would be fair"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67788.0,
      "end_time": 69735.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re looking over at your seatmate"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69759.0,
      "end_time": 73709.0,
      "text": "and wondering, \"What the hell does that have to do with architecture?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73733.0,
      "end_time": 77272.0,
      "text": "Well, all of these stories involved space"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78497.0,
      "end_time": 81425.0,
      "text": "and how it did or didn&#39;t accommodate us."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83134.0,
      "end_time": 84285.0,
      "text": "The fact is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84309.0,
      "end_time": 86235.0,
      "text": "we share some of our deepest connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86259.0,
      "end_time": 87523.0,
      "text": "in physical space."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88309.0,
      "end_time": 89712.0,
      "text": "And our stories play out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89736.0,
      "end_time": 93443.0,
      "text": "even in this crazy age of texting and tweeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93467.0,
      "end_time": 94730.0,
      "text": "in physical space."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96201.0,
      "end_time": 100330.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, architecture hasn&#39;t done a great job"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100580.0,
      "end_time": 102740.0,
      "text": "of telling all of our stories equally."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103491.0,
      "end_time": 107287.0,
      "text": "Too often, we see the building of monuments like the Gherkin"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107311.0,
      "end_time": 108692.0,
      "text": "or even Trump Tower ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108716.0,
      "end_time": 110357.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110749.0,
      "end_time": 114256.0,
      "text": "that tell the story of the haves rather than the have-nots."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115245.0,
      "end_time": 117130.0,
      "text": "Throughout my career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117370.0,
      "end_time": 118708.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve actively resisted the practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118732.0,
      "end_time": 121657.0,
      "text": "of building monuments to certain peoples&#39; stories --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121681.0,
      "end_time": 125230.0,
      "text": "usually white, male, rich --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125470.0,
      "end_time": 127512.0,
      "text": "and bulldozing other peoples&#39; stories --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127536.0,
      "end_time": 129235.0,
      "text": "usually people of color"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129258.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130728.00000000001,
      "text": "from low-income communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131857.0,
      "end_time": 133334.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve tried to create a practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133358.0,
      "end_time": 135376.0,
      "text": "that is rooted in elevating the stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135400.0,
      "end_time": 138196.0,
      "text": "of those who have most often been silenced."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139491.0,
      "end_time": 140641.0,
      "text": "That work --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141453.0,
      "end_time": 143667.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s been a mission in spatial justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144487.0,
      "end_time": 150458.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150482.0,
      "end_time": 152894.0,
      "text": "Now, spatial justice means that we understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152918.0,
      "end_time": 155545.0,
      "text": "that justice has a geography,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156977.0,
      "end_time": 162590.0,
      "text": "and that the equitable distribution of resources, services and access"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162614.0,
      "end_time": 164113.0,
      "text": "is a basic human right."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165426.0,
      "end_time": 167301.0,
      "text": "So what does spatial justice look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168161.0,
      "end_time": 170316.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;d like to share a story with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171703.0,
      "end_time": 173700.0,
      "text": "For years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173310.0,
      "end_time": 176188.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been working in the historically African-American neighborhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176212.0,
      "end_time": 178296.0,
      "text": "of Bayview Hunters Point in San Francisco,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178320.0,
      "end_time": 180583.0,
      "text": "on a plot of land that once held a power plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181418.0,
      "end_time": 182645.0,
      "text": "Back in the &#39;90s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182669.0,
      "end_time": 185739.0,
      "text": "a community group led by mothers who lived in the public housing"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185763.0,
      "end_time": 187315.0,
      "text": "on the hill above the plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187339.0,
      "end_time": 188668.0,
      "text": "fought for its closure."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189111.0,
      "end_time": 190261.0,
      "text": "They won."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190592.0,
      "end_time": 193335.0,
      "text": "The utility company finally tore it down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193359.0,
      "end_time": 194707.0,
      "text": "cleaned the soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 194731.0,
      "end_time": 196852.0,
      "text": "and capped most of the site with asphalt"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196876.0,
      "end_time": 199115.0,
      "text": "so that the clean soil wouldn&#39;t blow away."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199139.0,
      "end_time": 200956.0,
      "text": "Sounds like a success story, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202231.0,
      "end_time": 203381.0,
      "text": "Well, not so fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204342.0,
      "end_time": 207127.0,
      "text": "You see, because of various issues like land entitlements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207151.0,
      "end_time": 209180.0,
      "text": "lease agreements, etc.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209204.0,
      "end_time": 213155.0,
      "text": "the land actually couldn&#39;t be redeveloped for at least five to 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214337.0,
      "end_time": 217506.0,
      "text": "What that meant is that this community"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 217531.0,
      "end_time": 220793.0,
      "text": "that had been living near a power plant for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 220817.0,
      "end_time": 226642.0,
      "text": "now had 30 acres of asphalt in their backyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 227711.0,
      "end_time": 229251.0,
      "text": "To put that in context for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229275.0,
      "end_time": 232261.0,
      "text": "30 acres is equal to about 30 football fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 232909.0,
      "end_time": 236123.0,
      "text": "Now, the utility company didn&#39;t want to be the bad guy here."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236147.0,
      "end_time": 238415.0,
      "text": "Recognizing that they owed the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 238439.0,
      "end_time": 240439.0,
      "text": "they actually put out a call for designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 240463.0,
      "end_time": 242368.0,
      "text": "to propose temporary uses for this site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 242392.0,
      "end_time": 245267.0,
      "text": "hoping to turn it into a community benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245291.0,
      "end_time": 246652.0,
      "text": "rather than blight."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247351.0,
      "end_time": 251140.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m part of the diverse team of designers that responded to that call,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 251164.0,
      "end_time": 252500.0,
      "text": "and for the last four years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 252525.0,
      "end_time": 254525.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been collaborating with those mothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 254549.0,
      "end_time": 255700.0,
      "text": "and other residents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 255724.0,
      "end_time": 258694.0,
      "text": "as well as local organizations and the utility company."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 259394.0,
      "end_time": 262190.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been experimenting with all types of events"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262214.0,
      "end_time": 264730.0,
      "text": "to try and address issues of spatial justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 264754.0,
      "end_time": 267883.0,
      "text": "Everything from job training workshops"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267907.0,
      "end_time": 269635.0,
      "text": "to an annual circus"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 269659.0,
      "end_time": 271957.0,
      "text": "to even a beautiful, new shoreline trail."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 272511.0,
      "end_time": 274979.0,
      "text": "In the four years that we&#39;ve been operational,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275300.0,
      "end_time": 278964.0,
      "text": "over 12,000 people have come and done something on this site"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 278988.0,
      "end_time": 282422.0,
      "text": "that we hope has transformed their relationship to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 284115.0,
      "end_time": 285628.0,
      "text": "But lately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 285652.0,
      "end_time": 289217.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m starting to realize that events are not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290538.0,
      "end_time": 291688.0,
      "text": "A few months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 291712.0,
      "end_time": 294277.0,
      "text": "there was a community meeting in this neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294301.0,
      "end_time": 297366.0,
      "text": "The utility company was finally ready to talk concretely"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297390.0,
      "end_time": 299140.0,
      "text": "about long-term redevelopment."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 300280.0,
      "end_time": 303377.0,
      "text": "That meeting was kind of a disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 306562.0,
      "text": "There was a lot of yelling and anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306586.0,
      "end_time": 308166.0,
      "text": "People asked things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 308190.0,
      "end_time": 310190.0,
      "text": "\"If you&#39;re going to sell it to a developer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 310214.0,
      "end_time": 313126.0,
      "text": "wouldn&#39;t they just build luxury condos like everyone else?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 313150.0,
      "end_time": 314921.0,
      "text": "And \"Where has the city been?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 314945.0,
      "end_time": 317965.0,
      "text": "\"Why aren&#39;t there more jobs and resources in this neighborhood?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 319619.0,
      "end_time": 322762.0,
      "text": "It was not that our events had failed to bring joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 323935.0,
      "end_time": 326714.0,
      "text": "But in spite of that, there was still pain here."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 327995.0,
      "end_time": 330194.0,
      "text": "Pain from a history of environmental injustice"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330218.0,
      "end_time": 334150.0,
      "text": "that left many industrial uses in this neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 334174.0,
      "end_time": 336304.0,
      "text": "leaving residents living near toxic waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 336329.0,
      "end_time": 337832.0,
      "text": "and, literally, shit."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 339275.0,
      "end_time": 340561.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s pain from the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 340586.0,
      "end_time": 345288.0,
      "text": "that this zip code still has one of the lowest per capita income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 345312.0,
      "end_time": 346621.0,
      "text": "highest unemployment"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 346645.0,
      "end_time": 348301.0,
      "text": "and highest incarceration rates"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 348326.0,
      "end_time": 352751.0,
      "text": "in a city which tech giants like Twitter, Airbnb and Uber call home."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 353810.0,
      "end_time": 355507.0,
      "text": "And those tech companies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 355531.0,
      "end_time": 356816.0,
      "text": "hm --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 356840.0,
      "end_time": 359498.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve actually helped to trigger a gentrification push"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 359523.0,
      "end_time": 361620.0,
      "text": "that is rapidly redefining this neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 361644.0,
      "end_time": 363867.0,
      "text": "both in terms of identity and population."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 365299.0,
      "end_time": 368859.0,
      "text": "Now let me pause for a moment to talk about gentrification."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 370578.0,
      "end_time": 373626.0,
      "text": "I suspect for a lot of us, it&#39;s kind of like a dirty word."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 375350.0,
      "end_time": 377471.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s become synonymous with the displacement"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 377495.0,
      "end_time": 379492.0,
      "text": "of poor residents from their neighborhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 379516.0,
      "end_time": 380814.0,
      "text": "by wealthier newcomers."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 381355.0,
      "end_time": 383644.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;ve ever been displaced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 383668.0,
      "end_time": 386690.0,
      "text": "then you know the agony of losing a place that held your story."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 388176.0,
      "end_time": 390740.0,
      "text": "And if you haven&#39;t experienced this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 390764.0,
      "end_time": 394145.0,
      "text": "then I&#39;m going to ask you to try and imagine your way into it right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 395390.0,
      "end_time": 398532.0,
      "text": "Think about what it would be like to find your favorite local spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 398556.0,
      "end_time": 402234.0,
      "text": "a place where you often went and hung out with the old-timers or your friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 403486.0,
      "end_time": 404635.0,
      "text": "had vanished."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 405687.0,
      "end_time": 406838.0,
      "text": "And then you get home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 406862.0,
      "end_time": 408812.0,
      "text": "and you find a letter from your landlord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 408836.0,
      "end_time": 410746.0,
      "text": "saying that your rent&#39;s been doubled."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 411734.0,
      "end_time": 413289.0,
      "text": "The choice to stay --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 414301.0,
      "end_time": 415534.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not yours to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 416737.0,
      "end_time": 418543.0,
      "text": "You no longer belong in your home."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 420607.0,
      "end_time": 424686.0,
      "text": "And know that this feeling you&#39;re feeling right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 424710.0,
      "end_time": 426660.0,
      "text": "it would be the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 426900.0,
      "end_time": 429534.0,
      "text": "regardless of whether or not the person who harmed you meant to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 432190.0,
      "end_time": 435630.0,
      "text": "Developer Majora Carter once said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 435870.0,
      "end_time": 437509.0,
      "text": "\"Poor people don&#39;t hate gentrification."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 437533.0,
      "end_time": 440817.0,
      "text": "They just hate that they rarely get to hang around long enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 440841.0,
      "end_time": 442107.0,
      "text": "to enjoy its benefits.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 443970.0,
      "end_time": 449277.0,
      "text": "Why is it that we treat culture erasure and economic displacement as inevitable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 450930.0,
      "end_time": 452377.0,
      "text": "We could approach development"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 452401.0,
      "end_time": 455190.0,
      "text": "with an acknowledgment of past injustices --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 455430.0,
      "end_time": 457600.0,
      "text": "find value not only in those new stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 457300.0,
      "end_time": 458179.0,
      "text": "but the old ones, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 459145.0,
      "end_time": 462390.0,
      "text": "And make a commitment to build people&#39;s capacity to stay --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463681.0,
      "end_time": 465777.0,
      "text": "to stay in their homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 465801.0,
      "end_time": 467928.0,
      "text": "to stay in their communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 467952.0,
      "end_time": 469610.0,
      "text": "to stay where they feel whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 472297.0,
      "end_time": 474230.0,
      "text": "But to do this rethink,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 474470.0,
      "end_time": 477211.0,
      "text": "it requires looking at those past injustices"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 477235.0,
      "end_time": 479715.0,
      "text": "and the pain and grief that is interwoven into them."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 480474.0,
      "end_time": 483252.0,
      "text": "And as I started to reflect on my own work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 483276.0,
      "end_time": 486300.0,
      "text": "I realized that pain and grief have been recurring themes."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 487142.0,
      "end_time": 489771.0,
      "text": "I heard it early on in the Bayview Hunters Point project"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 489795.0,
      "end_time": 491676.0,
      "text": "when a man named Daryl said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 491700.0,
      "end_time": 494790.0,
      "text": "\"We&#39;ve always been set aside like an island --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 494103.0,
      "end_time": 495358.0,
      "text": "a no-man&#39;s-land.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 496780.0,
      "end_time": 498232.0,
      "text": "I also heard it in Houston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 498257.0,
      "end_time": 500591.0,
      "text": "when I was working on a project with day laborers."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 500615.0,
      "end_time": 503868.0,
      "text": "And as Juan told me stories of being robbed of his wages many times"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 503892.0,
      "end_time": 506400.0,
      "text": "on the corner in which he stood every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 506424.0,
      "end_time": 508995.0,
      "text": "to earn a living to support his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 509190.0,
      "end_time": 510170.0,
      "text": "he asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 510194.0,
      "end_time": 512924.0,
      "text": "\"Why can&#39;t anyone see the sacredness of this site?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 514756.0,
      "end_time": 517400.0,
      "text": "You know, you&#39;ve seen the pain, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 518604.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522337.00000000006,
      "text": "From campaigns around statue removals in Charlottesville and New Orleans ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 523796.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526130.0,
      "text": "to towns that have lost their industrial lifeblood"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 526154.0,
      "end_time": 527328.0,
      "text": "and are now dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 527352.0,
      "end_time": 529707.0,
      "text": "like Lorain, Ohio and Bolton, England."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 531212.0,
      "end_time": 534554.0,
      "text": "We often rush to remake these places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 534578.0,
      "end_time": 536788.0,
      "text": "thinking that we can ease their pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 538248.0,
      "end_time": 541180.0,
      "text": "But in our boundless desire to do good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 541204.0,
      "end_time": 542790.0,
      "text": "to get past all of our mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 542815.0,
      "end_time": 545338.0,
      "text": "to build places that hold possibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 546849.0,
      "end_time": 549734.0,
      "text": "we often maintain a blissful ignorance"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 550971.0,
      "end_time": 555866.0,
      "text": "of a landscape filled with a very long trail of broken promises"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 555890.0,
      "end_time": 557256.0,
      "text": "and squelched dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 558634.0,
      "end_time": 561860.0,
      "text": "We are building on top of brokenness."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 562763.0,
      "end_time": 565588.0,
      "text": "Is it any wonder that the foundations cannot hold?"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 567411.0,
      "end_time": 570695.0,
      "text": "Holding space for pain and grief was never part of my job description"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 570720.0,
      "end_time": 572250.0,
      "text": "as an architect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 572274.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "after all, it&#39;s not expedient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 574284.0,
      "end_time": 575856.0,
      "text": "focused on beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 575880.0,
      "end_time": 577847.0,
      "text": "and hell, even requested by my clients."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 580350.0,
      "end_time": 583496.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;ve seen what happens when there&#39;s space for pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 583520.0,
      "end_time": 585670.0,
      "text": "It can be transformational."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 586663.0,
      "end_time": 588179.0,
      "text": "Returning to our story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 588203.0,
      "end_time": 591347.0,
      "text": "when we first started working in the neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 591371.0,
      "end_time": 592800.0,
      "text": "one of the first things we did"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 592824.0,
      "end_time": 596612.0,
      "text": "was go out and interview the activists who had led the fight to close the plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 597195.0,
      "end_time": 600742.0,
      "text": "We consistently heard and felt from them a sense of impending loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 601480.0,
      "end_time": 603347.0,
      "text": "The neighborhood was already changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 603371.0,
      "end_time": 604521.0,
      "text": "even back then."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 604546.0,
      "end_time": 606594.0,
      "text": "People were leaving or dying of old age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 606618.0,
      "end_time": 609455.0,
      "text": "and with those departures, stories were being lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 610397.0,
      "end_time": 612354.0,
      "text": "To those activists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 612378.0,
      "end_time": 614793.0,
      "text": "no one was going to know the amazing things"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 614817.0,
      "end_time": 616970.0,
      "text": "that had happened in this community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 616994.0,
      "end_time": 619373.0,
      "text": "because to everyone on the outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 619397.0,
      "end_time": 620547.0,
      "text": "it was the ghetto."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 621468.0,
      "end_time": 622953.0,
      "text": "At worst, a place of violence;"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 622977.0,
      "end_time": 625389.0,
      "text": "at best, a blank slate."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 626682.0,
      "end_time": 628192.0,
      "text": "Neither was true, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 629344.0,
      "end_time": 632421.0,
      "text": "So my colleagues and I, we reached out to StoryCorps."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 633425.0,
      "end_time": 634575.0,
      "text": "And with their support,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 634600.0,
      "end_time": 636136.0,
      "text": "and that of the utility company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 636160.0,
      "end_time": 638400.0,
      "text": "we built a listening booth on our site."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 638459.0,
      "end_time": 640228.0,
      "text": "And we invited the residents to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 640252.0,
      "end_time": 642584.0,
      "text": "and have their stories recorded for posterity."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 643515.0,
      "end_time": 646124.0,
      "text": "After a few days of recording,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 646148.0,
      "end_time": 647449.0,
      "text": "we held a listening party"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 648695.0,
      "end_time": 649846.0,
      "text": "where we played clips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 649870.0,
      "end_time": 652419.0,
      "text": "much like what you hear on NPR every Friday morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 653625.0,
      "end_time": 655363.0,
      "text": "That party --"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 655387.0,
      "end_time": 657772.0,
      "text": "it was one of the most amazing community meetings"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 657797.0,
      "end_time": 659171.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve ever been a part of."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 659925.0,
      "end_time": 662163.0,
      "text": "In part because we didn&#39;t just talk about joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 663238.0,
      "end_time": 664461.0,
      "text": "but also pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 665833.0,
      "end_time": 667635.0,
      "text": "Two stories that I remember well --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 667659.0,
      "end_time": 670756.0,
      "text": "AJ talked about what it was like to grow up in the neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 670780.0,
      "end_time": 672505.0,
      "text": "There was always a kid to play with."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 673230.0,
      "end_time": 674891.0,
      "text": "But he also spoke with sadness"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 674915.0,
      "end_time": 678391.0,
      "text": "of what it was like to first be stopped and questioned by a police officer"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 678416.0,
      "end_time": 679566.0,
      "text": "when he was 11."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 681267.0,
      "end_time": 683596.0,
      "text": "GL also talked about the kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 683620.0,
      "end_time": 687396.0,
      "text": "and the ups and downs of the experience of living in this neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 687420.0,
      "end_time": 689135.0,
      "text": "but he also spoke with pride"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 689159.0,
      "end_time": 691603.0,
      "text": "of some of the organizations that had sprung up"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 691627.0,
      "end_time": 693992.0,
      "text": "to provide support and empowerment."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 694696.0,
      "end_time": 696156.0,
      "text": "He wanted to see more of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 697260.0,
      "end_time": 700867.0,
      "text": "By holding space to first express pain and grief,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 700891.0,
      "end_time": 703915.0,
      "text": "we were then able to brainstorm ideas for a site --"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 703939.0,
      "end_time": 708699.0,
      "text": "amazing ideas that then became the seeds of what we did over the next four years."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 709486.0,
      "end_time": 711544.0,
      "text": "So why the radically different meeting now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 712212.0,
      "end_time": 713362.0,
      "text": "Well ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 713700.0,
      "end_time": 717337.0,
      "text": "the pain and grief woven into these spaces was not created in a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 718164.0,
      "end_time": 720910.0,
      "text": "Healing also takes time."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 722328.0,
      "end_time": 726620.0,
      "text": "After all, who here thinks you can go to therapy just once and be cured?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 726644.0,
      "end_time": 728160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 728400.0,
      "end_time": 729189.0,
      "text": "Anyone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 730181.0,
      "end_time": 731352.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t think so."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 732135.0,
      "end_time": 733657.0,
      "text": "In retrospect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 733681.0,
      "end_time": 736535.0,
      "text": "I wish that we had held more listening sessions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 736559.0,
      "end_time": 738300.0,
      "text": "not just joyful events."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 739645.0,
      "end_time": 741771.0,
      "text": "My work&#39;s taken me all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 742916.0,
      "end_time": 747337.0,
      "text": "and I have yet to set foot in a place where pain didn&#39;t exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 747361.0,
      "end_time": 749728.0,
      "text": "and the potential for healing was absent."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 750311.0,
      "end_time": 753677.0,
      "text": "So while I&#39;ve spent my career honing my skills as an architect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 753701.0,
      "end_time": 755946.0,
      "text": "I realize that I&#39;m now also a healer."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 757869.0,
      "end_time": 761109.0,
      "text": "I suppose this is the point in the talk where I should be telling you"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 761133.0,
      "end_time": 762468.0,
      "text": "those five steps to healing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 762492.0,
      "end_time": 764180.0,
      "text": "but I don&#39;t have the solution --"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 764205.0,
      "end_time": 765544.0,
      "text": "yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 765568.0,
      "end_time": 766718.0,
      "text": "Just a path."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 767772.0,
      "end_time": 768923.0,
      "text": "That being said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 768947.0,
      "end_time": 771748.0,
      "text": "there are a few things I have learned along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 771772.0,
      "end_time": 772922.0,
      "text": "First --"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 773418.0,
      "end_time": 776350.0,
      "text": "we cannot create cities for everyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 776590.0,
      "end_time": 778693.0,
      "text": "unless we&#39;re first willing to listen to everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 779684.0,
      "end_time": 782351.0,
      "text": "Not just about what they hope to see built in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 782375.0,
      "end_time": 785255.0,
      "text": "but also about what has been lost or unfulfilled."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 786771.0,
      "end_time": 787920.0,
      "text": "Second --"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 788357.0,
      "end_time": 790906.0,
      "text": "healing is not just for \"those people.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 791969.0,
      "end_time": 794186.0,
      "text": "For those of us with privilege,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 794210.0,
      "end_time": 797833.0,
      "text": "we have to have a reckoning with our own guilt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 797857.0,
      "end_time": 800319.0,
      "text": "discomfort and complicity."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 801574.0,
      "end_time": 804740.0,
      "text": "As non-profit leader Anne Marks once observed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 804980.0,
      "end_time": 806300.0,
      "text": "\"Hurt people hurt people;"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 806325.0,
      "end_time": 808669.0,
      "text": "healed people heal people.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 810424.0,
      "end_time": 811574.0,
      "text": "And third --"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 812611.0,
      "end_time": 814802.0,
      "text": "healing is not about the erasure of pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 815822.0,
      "end_time": 819292.0,
      "text": "We often have a tendency to want to put a clean slate over our pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 819316.0,
      "end_time": 822194.0,
      "text": "much like that asphalt on the soil in Bayview Hunters Point."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 822602.0,
      "end_time": 824193.0,
      "text": "But it doesn&#39;t work that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 824768.0,
      "end_time": 827448.0,
      "text": "Healing is about acknowledging pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 827472.0,
      "end_time": 828721.0,
      "text": "and making peace with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 830484.0,
      "end_time": 834725.0,
      "text": "One of my favorite quotes says that healing renews our faith"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 834749.0,
      "end_time": 836489.0,
      "text": "in the process of becoming."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 837996.0,
      "end_time": 840254.0,
      "text": "I stand here before you as an architect-healer"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 840278.0,
      "end_time": 842998.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m ready to see what I can become,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 843220.0,
      "end_time": 845649.0,
      "text": "what my community and those that I work with can become,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 845673.0,
      "end_time": 846824.0,
      "text": "and what this country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 846848.0,
      "end_time": 849740.0,
      "text": "and frankly, this world can become."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 849990.0,
      "end_time": 851466.0,
      "text": "And I was not meant to take that journey alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 853202.0,
      "end_time": 857738.0,
      "text": "I believe that many of you are unhappy with the way that things are now."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 859202.0,
      "end_time": 861382.0,
      "text": "Believe that it can be different."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 862890.0,
      "end_time": 867260.0,
      "text": "I believe that you all are far more resilient than you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 868419.0,
      "end_time": 871690.0,
      "text": "But the first step requires courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 872343.0,
      "end_time": 874647.0,
      "text": "The courage to see each other&#39;s pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 875787.0,
      "end_time": 878713.0,
      "text": "and to be willing to stay in the presence of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 878737.0,
      "end_time": 880477.0,
      "text": "even when it gets uncomfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 881737.0,
      "end_time": 885427.0,
      "text": "Just imagine the change that we can make together"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 886428.0,
      "end_time": 888387.0,
      "text": "if we all committed to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 889323.0,
      "end_time": 890473.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 890498.0,
      "end_time": 897467.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}